Enlarge Animal or Plant

As the druid continues to develop his rapport with
nature, he becomes capable of infusing animals and
plants with life force, causing them to grow to
incredible size and strength.  This spell will make
an animal or plant-like creature much stronger.  Be
warned, however: it cannot be cast on a befriended
creature, or it would break the charm, so it must be
cast prior to befriend, making the charm more
difficult.  On the other hand, the more dangerous
creature will be worth more experience...

Command: enlarge <target> (defaults to attacker)
Base Cost: 35 SP
Base Recovery: medium
Base Effect: boost (all stats)
Base Duration: permanent
Guild Level: 1
